SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260702T124200Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261002T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 2 focus: Morning mobility\nShorter holds\, more movement b
	etween poses\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — Easy nasal b
	reathing\, neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip flexor\, ha
	mstring\, calf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Cat-cow\, chil
	d's pose\, gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area\; slow brea
	th\n\nInstagram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/reel/DW_zewYke
	et/\n\nTheme focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip and hamstring 
	openness\, breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:fcdfbd210ad757ca@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Shooting Session
DTSTAMP:20260702T124200Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261003T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 2 focus: Off the dribble\nCut inside\, laces drive\, 6–12 
	yards out\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (8 min) — Passing into space\, 
	light touches\n• Technique block (15 min) — Static ball — placement corner
	s\n• Movement finishes (15 min) — Receive-pass-shoot or dribble-cut-shoot\
	n• Pressure reps (10 min) — Time limit or consecutive goals\n• Cooldown (2
	 min) — Easy passes\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_dri
	ll_library.json or session_themes.json → shooting.instagramUrls\n\nTheme f
	ocus: striking technique\, placement\, off the dribble\, first-time finish
	es
LOCATION:Training Field / Goal
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
