BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:37473af8181f644c@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Running Session
DTSTAMP:20260702T124200Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270620T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 3 focus: Tempo run\n15–20 min comfortably hard — steady\, 
	no sprinting\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (10 min) — Easy jog\, dynami
	c stretch\, A-skips\n• Main set (25 min) — Intervals or steady tempo — see
	 weekly focus\n• Strides / accelerations (10 min) — 4–6 short bursts with 
	full walk-back recovery\n• Cooldown (5 min) — Easy jog or walk\, stretch c
	alves and hips\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_drill_li
	brary.json or session_themes.json → running.instagramUrls\n\nTheme focus: 
	aerobic base\, intervals\, tempo runs\, recovery pace\, soccer-specific co
	nditioning
LOCATION:Track / Field / Road
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
